headline: Intercontinental Exchange (ICE): Revisiting Valuation After Strong November 2025 Trading Volume and Open Interest Growth
summary: Intercontinental Exchange (ICE) just posted its November 2025 trading stats, and the picture is straightforward: higher volumes and open interest across key contracts that point to more activity on its platforms. See our latest analysis for Intercontinental Exchange. Against that backdrop, Intercontinental Exchange's share price now sits at $156.85, with a solid 1 month share price return of 7.73% but a softer 90 day share price return of minus 10.12%, highlighting momentum that is recovering...
